FeedPackage.Description: Common base functionality for all your projects. On PCL you get: Extensions for String, DateTime, Chat, Type, Dictionary and some regex patterns. On Net4 you get: Logs, session, configuration, autostart, config. Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.Core

FeedPackage.Title: OKHOSTING.Core

FeedPackage.Description:
Common base functionality for all your projects.
## PCL, usable from any device
* Base classes for extending Dictionary<,> and List<> * Extension methods for Type, String, Char, DateTime, XmlDocument and some others
## Net4
* Write log files * Set any executable to Autostart on user login * Shell proxy you can use to execute sequential command line commands * Send email with templates * Handle desktop/web user session's with the same code * Send email templates * Chek if there's an internet connection * Geolocalize an IP address * Create a Telnet connection * Reand / write your web.config settings
Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.Core

FeedPackage.Description:
Flexible, simple, feature complete, multi-database, multi-platform ORM. Works with any class, any naming convention, and most used databases.
## Features
* Works on top of OKHOSTING.Sql which give us access to MySql, SQLite and "DataBase web service" in mobile, and MySql, SQLite, SQL Server and PostgresSQL on desktop * Real POCOs, you don't need use "special classes", you can use any class you already have * Supports every database schema you want to use. You dont need a "special schema" * Supports any inheritance strategy you desire, and any one to many and many to many relationships you need * Class name and table name can be different, the same goes for properties and columns * Supports single and multi column primary keys, and foreign keys * You won't have to write SQL never again, unless you want to * Works on Windows, Linux, Mac, Android, iOS, Windows Phone and Universal Windows Platform * Allows you to create complex select operations, strongly typed, that include joins, limits, order, aggregated funcionts, group by * Very fast, light and small * Pretty easy to use
Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.ORM
FeedPackage.Summary: Flexible, simple, feature complete, multi-database, multi-platform ORM. Works with any class, any naming convention, and most used databases.
FeedPackage.Tags: okhosting orm sql sql generation database micro multiplatform xamarin android ois mac wpf windows forms asp.net web pcl
FeedPackage.Title: OKHOSTING.ORM

StackExpress Razor Documentation: http://razor.servicestack.net
- Turns ServiceStack into a Complete Web + REST Services Stack. Replaces need for ASP.NET MVC. - Runs In ASP.NET or Self-host, first-class cross-platform support on .NET / Mono runtimes. - Add HTML views to existing services. - Change Views and Layout templates at runtime. - No Ceremony development options - Pages without controllers, with typed and dynamic View Models. - Include Partial Markdown views in Razor pages. - Cascading Layout templates. - Pretty urls by default (no custom Routes needed). - Keep all views and assets together. - Smart View Pages.
FeedPackage.Summary: Provides ServiceStack's HTML Story including integrated support for MVC Razor's ViewEngine
FeedPackage.Tags: ServiceStack Razor ViewEngine View Templates Controllers Mono ASP.NET Self-Host

FeedPackage.Description:
Flexible, simple, feature complete, multi-database, multi-platform ORM. Works with any class, any naming convention, and most used databases.
## Features
* Works on top of OKHOSTING.Sql which give us access to MySql, SQLite and "DataBase web service" in mobile, and MySql, SQLite, SQL Server and PostgresSQL on desktop * Real POCOs, you don't need use "special classes", you can use any class you already have * Supports every database schema you want to use. You dont need a "special schema" * Supports any inheritance strategy you desire, and any one to many and many to many relationships you need * Class name and table name can be different, the same goes for properties and columns * Supports single and multi column primary keys, and foreign keys * You won't have to write SQL never again, unless you want to * Works on Windows, Linux, Mac, Android, iOS, Windows Phone and Universal Windows Platform * Allows you to create complex select operations, strongly typed, that include joins, limits, order, aggregated funcionts, group by * Very fast, light and small * Pretty easy to use
Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.ORM
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes: Fixed bug in DataBase.SelectInherited
FeedPackage.Summary: Flexible, simple, feature complete, multi-database, multi-platform ORM. Works with any class, any naming convention, and most used databases.
FeedPackage.Tags: okhosting orm crud sql sql generation database micro multiplatform xamarin android ois mac wpf windows forms asp.net web pcl
FeedPackage.Title: OKHOSTING.ORM

FeedPackage.Title: OKHOSTING.Sql

FeedPackage.Description:
Data acces library with a focus on portability, SQL generation and schema management
## PCL, usable from any device
* Generate SQL code for Create and Drop tables, columns, indexes, and foreign keys * Generate SQL code for Insert, Select, Delete, Update, Create and Drop operations, without writing SQL code yourself * Select operation is capable of using joins, aggregation, group by, sort, limit, pretty much everything supported * In conjunction with OKHOSTING.Sql.Net4.Web.Services (wich acts as a DataBase proxy), allows you to execute commands and read data from any device, using any supported database in the background
## Net4
* Generate SQL code specific for SqlServer * Execute commands and read data from SqlServer
Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.Sql

* Execute Create and Drop on tables, columns, indexes, and foreign keys * Execute Insert, Select, Delete, Update, Create and Drop operations, without writing SQL code yourself * Select operation is capable of using joins, aggregation, group by, sort, limit, pretty much everything supported
Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.Sql

FeedPackage.Description:
Android MySql data acces library with a with MySql-specific SQL code generation, schema management and executing commannds on the DataBase
## Android
* Generate SQL code for Create and Drop tables, columns, indexes, and foreign keys * Generate SQL code for Insert, Select, Delete, Update, Create and Drop operations, without writing SQL code yourself * Select operation is capable of using joins, aggregation, group by, sort, limit, pretty much everything supported * Generate SQL code specific for MySql * Execute commands and read data from MySql
* Alternatively you can use OKHOSTING.Sql.Net4.Web.Services (wich acts as a DataBase proxy), allows you to execute commands and read data from any device, using any supported database in the background
Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.Sql

FeedPackage.Description:
Motherfucking cool multi-platform UI framework. Create your apps once on PCL and have your UI generated on runtime for ASP.NET, Windows Forms, WPF, Linux (Mono + WinForms), Mac OS (Mono + WinForms and Xamarin.Mac), iOS, Android, Windows Phone (via Xamarin.Forms) and Windows Universal Platform.
## Features
* Create your apps in PCL and run them everywhere, truly multi-platform (web included) * The UI is defined from code (XAML designer on the way) * 100% native controls are used in all platforms * You have only the "common" UI api surface among all platforms * Supports click, doble click and, for user input controls, value changed events * Using OKHOSTING.UI.CSS you can use CSS files to define the styles of your controls on all platforms (thanks to AngleSharp)
## Supported controls
### Regular controls
* Autocomplete * Button * Calendar * CheckBox * HyperLink * Image * Label * ListPicker (equivalent to a DropDownList) * PasswordTextBox * TextArea * TextBox
### Forms
* Create forms for user data input/output * Create form fields for string, int, decimal, date, enum, bool, xml or any custom type you need * Create forms to execute a method
Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.UI
FeedPackage.Summary: Data acces library with a focus on portability, SQL generation and schema management
FeedPackage.Tags: okhosting ui user interface multiplatform xamarin android ois mac wpf windows forms asp.net web pcl

FeedPackage.Description:
Open source multi-platform UI framework. Create your apps once on PCL and have your UI generated on runtime for ASP.NET, Windows Forms, WPF, Linux (Mono + WinForms), Mac OS (Mono + WinForms and Xamarin.Mac), iOS, Android, Windows Phone (via Xamarin.Forms) and Windows Universal Platform.
## Features
* Create your apps in PCL and run them everywhere, truly multi-platform (web included) * The UI is defined from code (XAML designer on the way) * 100% native controls are used in all platforms * You have only the "common" UI api surface among all platforms * Supports click, doble click and, for user input controls, value changed events * Using OKHOSTING.UI.CSS you can use CSS files to define the styles of your controls on all platforms (thanks to AngleSharp)
## Supported controls
### Regular controls
* Autocomplete * Button * Calendar * CheckBox * HyperLink * Image * Label * ListPicker (equivalent to a DropDownList) * PasswordTextBox * TextArea * TextBox
### Forms
* Create forms for user data input/output * Create form fields for string, int, decimal, date, enum, bool, xml or any custom type you need * Create forms to execute a method
Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.UI
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes: * Added Forms.BinaryField for binary data
FeedPackage.Summary: Open source multi-platform UI framework. Create your apps once on PCL and have your UI generated on runtime for ASP.NET, Windows Forms, WPF, Linux (Mono + WinForms), Mac OS (Mono + WinForms and Xamarin.Mac), iOS, Android, Windows Phone (via Xamarin.Forms) and Windows Universal Platform.
FeedPackage.Tags: okhosting ui user interface multiplatform xamarin android ois mac wpf windows forms asp.net web pcl

Open source multi-platform UI framework. Create your apps once on PCL and have your UI generated on runtime for ASP.NET, Windows Forms, WPF, Linux (Mono + WinForms), Mac OS (Mono + WinForms and Xamarin.Mac), iOS, Android, Windows Phone (via Xamarin.Forms) and Windows Universal Platform.
## Features
* Create your apps in PCL and run them everywhere, truly multi-platform (web included) * The UI is defined from code (XAML designer on the way) * 100% native controls are used in all platforms * You have only the "common" UI api surface among all platforms * Supports click, doble click and, for user input controls, value changed events * Using OKHOSTING.UI.CSS you can use CSS files to define the styles of your controls on all platforms (thanks to AngleSharp)
## Supported controls
### Regular controls
* Autocomplete * Button * Calendar * CheckBox * HyperLink * Image * Label * ListPicker (equivalent to a DropDownList) * PasswordTextBox * TextArea * TextBox
### Forms
* Create forms for user data input/output * Create form fields for string, int, decimal, date, enum, bool, xml or any custom type you need * Create forms to execute a method
Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.UI

* Create your apps in PCL and run them everywhere, truly multi-platform (web included) * The UI is defined from code (XAML designer on the way) * 100% native controls are used in all platforms * You have only the "common" UI api surface among all platforms * Supports click, doble click and, for user input controls, value changed events * Using OKHOSTING.UI.CSS you can use CSS files to define the styles of your controls on all platforms (thanks to AngleSharp)
## Supported controls
* Autocomplete * Button * Calendar * CheckBox * HyperLink * Image * Label * ListPicker (equivalent to a DropDownList) * PasswordTextBox * TextArea * TextBox
Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.UI

Motherfucking cool multi-platform UI framework. Create your apps once on PCL and have your UI generated on runtime for ASP.NET, Windows Forms, WPF, Linux (Mono + WinForms), Mac OS (Mono + WinForms and Xamarin.Mac), iOS, Android, Windows Phone (via Xamarin.Forms) and Windows Universal Platform.
## Features
* Create your apps in PCL and run them everywhere, truly multi-platform (web included) * The UI is defined from code (XAML designer on the way) * 100% native controls are used in all platforms * You have only the "common" UI api surface among all platforms * Supports click, doble click and, for user input controls, value changed events * Using OKHOSTING.UI.CSS you can use CSS files to define the styles of your controls on all platforms (thanks to AngleSharp)
## Supported controls
* Autocomplete * Button * Calendar * CheckBox * HyperLink * Image * Label * ListPicker (equivalent to a DropDownList) * PasswordTextBox * TextArea * TextBox
Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.UI

Open source multi-platform UI framework. Create your apps once on PCL and have your UI generated on runtime for ASP.NET, Windows Forms, WPF, Linux (Mono + WinForms), Mac OS (Mono + WinForms and Xamarin.Mac), iOS, Android, Windows Phone (via Xamarin.Forms) and Windows Universal Platform.
## Features
* Create your apps in PCL and run them everywhere, truly multi-platform (web included) * The UI is defined from code (XAML designer on the way) * 100% native controls are used in all platforms * You have only the "common" UI api surface among all platforms * Supports click, doble click and, for user input controls, value changed events * Using OKHOSTING.UI.CSS you can use CSS files to define the styles of your controls on all platforms (thanks to AngleSharp)
## Supported controls
* Autocomplete * Button * Calendar * CheckBox * HyperLink * Image * Label * ListPicker (equivalent to a DropDownList) * PasswordTextBox * TextArea * TextBox
Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.UI
